{"tid":430132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！！！我懷疑老豆係廁所食大麻","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T04:53:46.000Z","uid":145922,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"976a46dfd41591c40b3ce88d777d8861350ac2c0","tid":430132,"uid":145922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，是咁的呢幾日我老豆冇返工，我就冇嘢做留係屋企，咁我見佢有時入左廁所後出黎都好似on下on下咁，扶住個鞋櫃摸個燈制都要成半分鐘。<br />\n一開始我都冇咩留意，諗住佢應該係唔舒服姐。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢平時都係想吃煙個時都盡量走入廚房or廁所，之不過呢兩日佢經常好似自言自語咁，講嘢好似1999，份人突然古靈精怪禁，一時好似冇咩精神係禁訓，一時好似冇咩事咁。所以我特別留意佢，啱啱佢入完廁所，我就順便入去放水跟住我聞到陣煙味，但一定唔係佢平時陣煙味。同埋我老媽子係廁所搵到呢支嘢。點算呀我宜家好驚，成身震曬。<br />\nSorry for1999<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/215931_f05e7ad5006caa598644f8585f148018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F215931_f05e7ad5006caa598644f8585f148018.jpg&h=fdecaa94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/215933_e80cbc940f729fa39d02dafeb702b5ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F215933_e80cbc940f729fa39d02dafeb702b5ee.jpg&h=e8446e16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c610c5b54d48f84af490f8e8a467f73627e20ee","tid":430132,"uid":53794,"like":45,"dislike":10,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"大麻有乜好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2c6936bcec2a4d7b9e79a27b6cfa2517068178","tid":430132,"uid":20448,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"我有朋友都係食自己捲既煙 都似呢種<br />\n唔一定係大麻既"},{"pid":"4f1ac7407d9a5355e585fc109c1bd5150827c0c4","tid":430132,"uid":34444,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"推到佢坐監啦等乜"},{"pid":"e56da7c6a0a3d0d430b6f8bbc33d618f7242de22","tid":430132,"uid":17055,"like":22,"dislike":19,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:05:25.